,"tid":2061483,"uid":119667,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-21T15:27:28.000Z","msg":"好驚有人睇緊戲問問題<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7d58a6cf9c0cfa2143139c1b4ce808eb018f14e6","tid":2061483,"uid":111398,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-21T15:45:39.000Z","msg":"一個人睇戲真係好爽 唔駛就人喜好<br />\n睇咩片幾時睇邊度睇自己話哂事 尤其啲冷門戲<br />\n可能因為身邊朋友唔太好睇戲 除左商業大片之外<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n好耐以前會怕柒 睇多一兩次就鐘意左一個人<br />\n有時同著個鐘意講野既朋友睇戲仲死<br />\n一黎嘈住自己 二黎嘈到其他人覺得尷尬<br />\n不過喜劇啊動畫嗰啲搵人一齊睇開心啲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n同埋喺戲院黑媽媽當係俾自己一個喘息空間都幾舒服，有時候睇完啲沉重或者議題複雜既電影其實唔係好想講野，想自己慢慢沉澱下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b2d4d18553cca3cda96757570a47ea29f2191615","tid":2061483,"uid":44269,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-24T17:32:41.000Z","msg":"星期二2：00既時候得我一個<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n返而隔離院  好鬼多人<br />\n好似有一種奇妙既感覺....<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/LR6FeLt.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FLR6FeLt.jpg&h=b5bfb03b&s={SIZE}\" />"}]}